{"tid":1717741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［中大人入］中大戰役應對之策","createTime":"2019-11-13T16:31:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T14:17:13.000Z","uid":3766,"like":13,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fa5b88e082d71d444568d53f56c96a02f8fc6d23","tid":1717741,"uid":3766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:31:23.000Z","msg":"我頭先發左咁嘅夢，以下係我喺夢境聽到嘅神的啟示 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中大今日已經完sem，但各位中大人依然死守中大，對守護中大嘅強烈意志實在令人敬佩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但而家繼續留守中大嘅話，結果唔難預見：<br />\n學生處於被動狀態，對家乘虛而入，全力將中大學生置諸死地！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解對方對中大咁鍥而不捨？<br />\n因為中大具有象徵性意義，「暴大」並非浪得虛名，但一旦拿下咗暴大，即可重創我方軍心，其餘幾間大學立即潰不成軍，對方不戰而勝。<br />\n而缺少咗投入度最高嘅大學、大專生後，餘下嘅只係星斗市民，不難對付。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有見及此，要避免悲劇發生喺中大同埋全港，就一定要全力保存中大！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n毛主席喺1947年撤離延安有云：「存人失地，人地皆存；存地失人，人地皆失。作戰不在於一城一地的得失，主要是消滅敵人的有生力量。」<br />\n<br />\n要保存中大，並非以中大人嘅肉血之軀去保護中大校園；應該係保存所有中大人嘅實力，迅速撤離中大校園並廣告天下，他日再重返校園，齊齊開sem！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家已經完sem，中大學生齊齊離開校園實在再正常不過，如果對方要強攻一個冇學生嘅大學校園只會落得被世人唾罵嘅下場，相反學生則可以齊上齊落，重奪主導權<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n兵貴神速，希望各位中大人可以考慮以上建議，儘快行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能你覺得咁做條氣唔順，但呢家唔係意氣之爭嘅時候，保留實力點都好過送頭呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中大人！行動！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2beab67002df53c22992e3f59866c81f91aed180","tid":1717741,"uid":7549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:36:55.000Z","msg":"推！希望暴大學生操體能時，可以考慮下唔同戰略！<br />\n<br />\n武運昌隆！"},{"pid":"fa37e35bf86faff45ef49fc03c4a1bd284194df6","tid":1717741,"uid":3766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:40:02.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f1d4d9536544aa6f900e28f004568176c7f222","tid":1717741,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:49:16.000Z","msg":"五毛分化狗有風向：放棄扼守要道既大學，守=嘉年華<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1717765\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1717765</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a05ad5947381caee495899ae38e3a1f09ede0986","tid":1717741,"uid":3766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:56:56.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔係五毛呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a299a70f804f58b19098cc9175d96a0ec80504","tid":1717741,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:46:08.000Z","msg":"我咁覺得啦...正苦今日1113擺明想拖中大<br />\n咁如果班狗點都要攻入中大, 入面冇晒人冇野可charge既情況下, 咁校方同社會唔係有更大既理由去譴責黑警濫暴?"},{"pid":"c9520daed2b52cf5dd687f1eff8509d0b49b629b","tid":1717741,"uid":3766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T23:40:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa3a9b0ae587e614d5912929b47a7ea5b2fa8e13","tid":1717741,"uid":3766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:07:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d354d854b98c0e2d046db4ca06fe0b5242a22fb","tid":1717741,"uid":3766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:24:45.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52c259bd00a4ba4a9bc356917e83e69de69efa10","tid":1717741,"uid":3766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:58:52.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1de65e4bc840056226743ecd06840a95b52f694b","tid":1717741,"uid":3766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:04:15.000Z","msg":